      "raceComments": "{\"comment\":\"2. MOONLIGHT NELLIE could not have been more impressive last start in her strong 17.61 win at this track in a Maiden over 305m. Top win latest and looms as the one to beat again. 1. APPELLANT doesn't have the best strike-rate. Better run when finding the frame last time though, finishing second (23.26) at this track. Has never been out of the money in four starts this course and distance. The form from his last run stacks up well. Must be included in calculations. 8. GALACTIC NEUTRON broke a string of placings finishing in the money two on end before a last start fifth (23.36) at this track. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings four times from eight starts. Has ability and a bold showing is expected. 6. NATURALLY GIRL was in the money last start and likely to feature again.\",\"runners\":[2,1,8,6],\"exclusive\":false}",
